column5: Heard about some new bedding for leeches, with this bedding could you bring them into Canada?
Heard that the only reason Leeches were prohibited was the water they were in.

Rationale for the ban was worded "The unrestricted import of leeches posed a risk of introducing new species of leeches to the province, as well as additional animals and plants that can be carried in leech holding water."
